name: Pictureplane
description: '''Travis James Egedy''' (born May 1, 1985),{{Primary source inline|date=February 2020}} better known by his stage name '''Pictureplane''', is an American [[electronic music|electronic]] musician, visual artist and fashion designer based in [[Brooklyn]], New York. He first appeared in the music scene of [[Denver]], Colorado, making a name for himself at Rhinoceropolis, the DIY space where he also lived. He has been credited for coining the term "[[witch house (genre)|witch house]]". He is also a founder of the fashion brand Alien Body.
